Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.20,0:00:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳 愛到出神陶醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.20,0:00:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳 愛到懊惱萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.05,0:00:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.55,0:00:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳 無法忘記妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.59,0:00:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風兒硬是拆開\N我們纏綿甜蜜的吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.77,0:00:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面對無法停止的熾熱心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.04,0:00:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.94,0:00:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人無法討厭的冷漠態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.15,0:00:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,見不到面令我痛苦萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.15,0:01:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳鬱悶不樂的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.29,0:01:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我心碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.06,0:01:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.27,0:01:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.48,0:01:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.67,0:01:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,還在講電話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.90,0:01:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼重要的時候\N到底在幹什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.64,0:02:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,你在打給誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.55,0:02:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打給郁子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.08,0:02:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.99,0:02:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我講一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.49,0:02:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,郁子嗎?\N叫妳爺爺來聽電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.46,0:02:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?什麼?妳說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.03,0:02:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十塊錢,十塊錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.43,0:02:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有這個必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.83,0:02:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無老伯因為學校理事會的旅行\N到香港去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.57,0:02:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.31,0:02:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,他什麼時候回來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說是後天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.48,0:02:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽,郁子說他們家沒有在談\N要拆掉這棟公寓的事唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.03,0:03:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#51 四谷也震驚不已!\N一刻館消失的日子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.21,0:03:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之,在我公公回來之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.05,0:03:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我們悶不吭聲乖乖的等嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.08,0:03:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.72,0:03:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果他回來說“事情就是這樣沒錯”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.79,0:03:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時候該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.42,0:03:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真遺憾,我原本還很相信\N這個房東一定不會做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.26,0:03:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情又還沒有決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.26,0:03:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說啊\N郁子她爸媽也說不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.80,0:03:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定是她爺爺\N一個人在私下進行著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.21,0:03:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你居然能這麼冷靜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.71,0:03:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一刻館被拆的話\N最頭痛的人應該是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.15,0:03:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟管理員之間的聯繫\N只有一刻館而已唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.99,0:04:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之,大家分頭去找傳聞的來源吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贊成,贊成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.73,0:04:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是個好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也只能那麼做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.90,0:04:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天我也去\N我們的不動產公司問問看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.01,0:04:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也要幫忙喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.48,0:04:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不好意思\N才剛搬來就碰到這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.91,0:04:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會,妳應該比我們更擔心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.22,0:04:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就這樣囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.69,0:04:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家來飲酒作樂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.53,0:04:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.93,0:04:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時候你們在想什麼啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.57,0:04:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要那麼正經八百嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.52,0:05:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果不動產公司也沒聽說\N一刻館要拆除的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.76,0:05:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,他們倒說了一件\N很奇怪的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼奇怪的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.40,0:05:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從一刻館再稍微往上走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一棟跟我們很像的公寓\N不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.84,0:05:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.54,0:05:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裡的房東去年過世了\N兒子繼承了他的財產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.51,0:05:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說他兒子要把公寓拆掉\N改建成大樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.29,0:05:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是把要拆的那棟公寓\N錯以為是一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.39,0:05:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據我得到的消息\N要拆除的是一刻館,錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是聽誰說的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工作上的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.90,0:05:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼工作?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不能告訴你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,消息千真萬確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.54,0:05:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來,來這裡喝酒的客人\N大家也只說一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並沒有說其它的公寓名稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.45,0:06:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,整件事到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.17,0:06:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,又是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.08,0:06:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次很不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.75,0:06:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要去喝杯咖啡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓您久等了,請慢用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於拆除的傳聞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.93,0:06:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我去加油站的時候\N聽到其他客人在說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.43,0:06:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們有明確的說是一刻館嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.17,0:07:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們說一刻館附近的土地\N現在可以賣到多少錢之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.55,0:07:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳聞是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.85,0:07:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都不知道從何查起\N所以感到很困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一個傳聞呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.89,0:07:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.13,0:07:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無小姐再婚的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.10,0:07:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.04,0:07:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全是捏造的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.04,0:07:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很想這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,還不能確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.36,0:07:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.10,0:08:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這顆哈蜜瓜\N三越先生說要請大家吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.27,0:08:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他的客人帶來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.51,0:08:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,客人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.68,0:08:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,等一下一起吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,一刻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.74,0:08:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽過MHT嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.38,0:08:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一家叫“MYH0MET0WN”的\N不動產公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.95,0:08:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.89,0:09:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個叫三越的人\N經常在那家公司的新宿分店進出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.26,0:09:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是怎麼知道的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.23,0:09:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那家公司\N就在我放學回家的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.74,0:09:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我突然想起有急事要辦\N不好意思,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.66,0:10:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才在門口跟你擦身而過的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.26,0:10:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是三越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.56,0:10:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹,快點把車開走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.43,0:10:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.85,0:10:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果小津江說的是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.58,0:10:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,結果那家公司怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.42,0:10:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺蠻詭異的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.52,0:10:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我一說出時鐘坡這個名字\N他們就開始警戒了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.33,0:10:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,那麼三越\N是MHT派來的間諜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.84,0:10:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們去那家公司看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.61,0:10:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正現在三越還在裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.24,0:11:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,還是等一下比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.58,0:11:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先要通知音無小姐才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.12,0:11:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,萬一他真的打算騙我們的話\N先通知音無小姐比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.45,0:11:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.12,0:11:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是三越先生受那家\N不動產公司之託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.39,0:11:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到處散播那個謠言嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.16,0:11:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.22,0:11:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,可以確定的是\N背後應該有什麼陰謀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.16,0:11:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三越先生不是那種人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.13,0:11:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是那種會平白無故\N出賣別人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他明明去了那家公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.64,0:12:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定有什麼原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.74,0:12:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定是我們誤會了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們說的我都懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.45,0:12:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會直接去找他問問看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.16,0:12:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.66,0:12:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好歹也是個管理員\N聽得出什麼是謊話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.66,0:12:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前\N請先不要跟四谷他們說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.56,0:12:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賢太郎,吃飯囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-我走了\N-好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.77,0:13:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個傳聞一定是假的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.81,0:13:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧,郁子的爺爺\N不會做那麼惡劣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.12,0:13:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯\N媽媽,吃飯吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.62,0:13:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很想相信他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你啊,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.40,0:13:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在等賣豆腐的來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.97,0:14:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好慢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.84,0:14:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?\N你不是說什麼要去上廁所的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.51,0:14:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,現在已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.01,0:14:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以上一樓的廁所\N衛生紙會減少的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.18,0:14:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下可能會下雨喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不上樓去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正要上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.74,0:14:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是請大家吃的\N車站前的章魚燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.94,0:14:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.64,0:14:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.95,0:14:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有點事想跟你談一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.22,0:15:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個我拿去分給大家吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.84,0:15:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,被他們看見啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.51,0:15:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我想問問到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照這樣下去,你也不會舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.75,0:15:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.52,0:15:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的確經常去那個地方\N不過是以客人的身分去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.69,0:15:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實,我是在那裡出生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.93,0:15:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前那一帶都是矮房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.57,0:15:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我家前面還有一條\N從角苦到九段的路面電車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.11,0:15:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已經都不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.84,0:16:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次想到我老家就位在那棟大樓\N總是覺得很懷念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.57,0:16:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳相信我說的話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.21,0:16:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很感謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裡,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.28,0:16:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你在這裡住久一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.09,0:16:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡真是個好地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.03,0:16:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是個好地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.44,0:17:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能,他也太會掰了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.94,0:17:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是看起來不像在說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己去問他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.69,0:17:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個在這裡幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.65,0:17:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,賴皮鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,進來跟我們喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.79,0:17:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下,我要去找三越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.69,0:17:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔,他沒有來耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.76,0:17:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三越,章魚燒快吃光囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.77,0:17:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一之瀨太太\N三越先生去澡堂洗澡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.04,0:17:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼嘛\N沒辦法,我們先吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.06,0:17:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隔天早上\N來了一封發信者不明的電報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.96,0:17:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是給三越的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.17,0:18:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面寫著“立刻來上班!”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三越,三越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.41,0:18:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不在嗎?有你的電報喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.51,0:18:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有回應嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.81,0:18:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.01,0:18:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從後窗什麼都看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.92,0:18:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.98,0:18:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.70,0:18:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只留下一桶酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.31,0:18:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是懂得做人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.15,0:18:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,拆除的事果然是假的囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.29,0:18:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是假的\N我怎麼可能會背著妳做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.66,0:19:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,為什麼會有那種謠言呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.06,0:19:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是聽郁子說了之後\N嚇了一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.97,0:19:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,只要我還有一口氣在\N絕對不會讓任何人在那裡蓋大樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.35,0:19:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(MY HOME TOWN 不動產)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.40,0:19:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說,他果然是\N那家公司派來的間諜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.97,0:19:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,他不是那家公司的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.14,0:19:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說是應業界要求\N到處探勘大樓建設用地的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.55,0:19:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他明明看起來像是個\N連蟲都不會殺的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.35,0:19:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,如果是四谷的話\N我還能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.92,0:20:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只會做討別人歡心的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.42,0:20:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還真敢說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.56,0:20:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過管理員,下次有新房客進來\N一定要謹慎點才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.97,0:20:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管我們怎麼親切對待他\N到頭來還不被他耍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.21,0:20:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許那是他來這裡的真正目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.98,0:20:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,他一定有苦衷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.08,0:20:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再說,我們也沒有什麼損失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.98,0:20:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這點讓我覺得很不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.62,0:20:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可思議?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.95,0:20:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,聽說今天早上\N他有打電話去那家公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.29,0:20:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只說了一句“我要退出”\N就掛電話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.10,0:20:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退出?退出一刻館的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.77,0:20:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店裡的人氣得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.94,0:20:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說,那通電報是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.71,0:20:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他回不了那家公司了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.86,0:21:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的東西誕生時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舊的東西會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.96,0:21:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消失或許是無可奈何的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.47,0:21:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但絕對不能忘記消失的東西\N我是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.84,0:21:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些話是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.81,0:21:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是三越對我說過的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.18,0:21:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.59,0:21:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的,在附近的公園說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.42,0:21:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三越啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.78,0:22:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來\N那桶酒看起來好像很不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.61,0:22:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.88,0:22:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.32,0:22:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以喝吧,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.42,0:22:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.25,0:22:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就喝酒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.49,0:22:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,借你的房間喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.46,0:22:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有得喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.89,0:22:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽,晚飯怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.23,0:22:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吃泡麵啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.27,0:22:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不去喝酒嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.77,0:22:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.51,0:22:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三越看來是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.45,0:22:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這裡住的都是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.72,0:22:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹嘛,我們在等你們耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.32,0:22:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點來,酒會被喝光喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.95,0:22:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,真的要被四谷喝光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.56,0:22:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託,這是人家的酒耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.36,0:22:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我拿到的酒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.46,0:22:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你個頭啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.60,0:23:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些人是好人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.04,0:23:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想喝一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.57,0:23:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,三鷹也來喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.84,0:23:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.61,0:23:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無小姐也一起來喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.35,0:23:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊,請你們先去吧\N我把這個火處理一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.82,0:23:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.45,0:23:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都四年了,真快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.92,0:23:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事我辦不到\N我無法忘記惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.39,0:23:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.92,0:24:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「惣一郎請原諒我!\N響子含淚的再婚宣言!」
