Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.37,0:24:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使夢醒了\N依然在心頭蕩漾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.01,0:24:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.55,0:24:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.33,0:24:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.17,0:24:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.74,0:24:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.08,0:24:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.98,0:24:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.72,0:25:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.89,0:25:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平靜的合聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.90,0:25:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使擁抱著妳依然惆悵滿懷
